msgid "Scenario V: Return to For the Greater Good"
msgstr "冒险V：重返崇高利益"

msgid "Choose one of the two Lounge locations at random. Put the Lodge Catacombs and the chosen Lounge into play. Remove the other version of the Lounge from the game."
msgstr "从2个休息室地点中随机选择1个地点。将秘社地下墓穴和所选的休息室放置入场。将休息室的另一版本从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at the Lodge Gates."
msgstr "每位调查员从秘社大门开始游戏。"

msgid "Set each other remaining location aside, out of play (Library, Vault, Inner Sanctum, Hidden Passageway, and the 3 Sanctum Doorway locations)."
msgstr "将所有剩余地点(藏书室、机密室、圣堂内室、隐秘通道、3张圣堂门廊)放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of the scenario, the following additional rules apply:\n"
"\"The <b>Objective</b> on Act 3a is optional.\n"
"After all other ([skull]/[cultist]/[tablet]/[elder_thing]) keys have been put into play, if another effect would cause a set-aside key to be put into play, use another unused (+/-) chaos token instead of putting no key into play.\n"
"At the end of the scenario, add each (+/-) chaos token controlled by an investigator to the victory display. Each one is worth <b>Victory 1</b>.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to For the Greater Good card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"在本场冒险接下来的时间里，增加以下额外规则：\n"
"“场景3a上的<b>目标</b>是可选的。\n"
"在所有其他的([skull]/[cultist]/[tablet]/[elder_thing])钥匙都已被放置入场后，如果有另一效果将要导致一个放在一边的钥匙被放置入场，改为使用另一个未被使用的(+/-)混乱标记，而不是不放置钥匙入场。\n"
"当冒险结束时，将所有受调查员控制的(+/-)混乱标记加入胜利牌区。每个标记价值<b>胜利1</b>。”\n"
"将重返崇高利益卡牌叠加到冒险辅助卡上，以作提示。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hierophant · V\" in the reversed position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是逆位的“教皇·V”。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hierophant · V\" in the upright position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是正位的“教皇·V”。"
